                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4537" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0655</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8312 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">遭遇新金融工具准则，朗源股份会计差错更正后的万般无奈</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Encountering New Financial Instrument Standards, Lontrue Co., Ltd. Has No Choice but to Correct Its Accounting Errors</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，陈思涵，陆叶，阎蓓蓓</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朗源股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新金融工具准则；可供出售金融资产；权益性工具投资；朗源股份</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> New Financial Instrument Standard; Financial Assets Available for Sale; Equity Instrument Investment; Lontrue Co., ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年1月1日实施的新金融工具准则中金融资产分类由“四分类”调整为“三分类”，上市公司原先利用可供出售金融资产来进行利润调节的方式骤然失去用武之地。本案例中朗源股份将所持有的永辉超市的股份划分为可供出售金融资产，并在过去多次出售实现报表利润调节，而在2019年欲故技重施时，却无奈遭遇新金融工具准则的要求，最终只能出具会计差错更正公告。本案例旨在通过对朗源股份案例的介绍，引导学员掌握新金融工具准则的分类方法及相应金融资产的核算方法。对比新旧准则下的相关处理，讨论和思考新准则如何能更好地规范上市公司利用金融资产的分类进行盈余管理的行为，从而提高学生的分析和决策能力，对研究新金融工具准则的落地实施及后续监管都具有重要的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the new financial instrument standards implemented on January 1, 2019, the classification of financial assets was changed from &quot;four categories&quot; to &quot;three categories&quot;. The previously available financial assets for sale by listed companies for profit adjustment suddenly lost their usefulness. In this case, Lontrue Co., ltd. divided the shares it held in yonghui supermarket into financial assets that could be sold, and realized profit adjustment in statements after several sales in the past. However, when it wanted to repeat the old way in 2019, it had no alternative but to meet the requirements of the new financial instrument standards, so it could only issue a notice to correct accounting errors. The purpose of this case is to guide students to master the classification method of new financial instrument criteria and the accounting method of corresponding financial assets through the introduction of Lontrue’ case. By comparing the relevant treatment under the old and new criteria, this paper discusses and considers how the new criteria can better regulate the behavior of listed companies in earnings management based on the classification of financial assets, so as to improve students&#39; ability of analysis and decision-making, which is of great reference significance for the study on the implementation of the new criteria for financial instruments and the subsequent supervision.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新旧金融工具准则的差别、金融资产的分类与后续计量及其对企业报表的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
